        "title": "How to use calendar to create date",
        "body": "<p>i need to use Calendar to create date at which i specify the month , the week number and the day of week.\ni am creating new instance of calendar:\n**<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Calendar c = Calendar.getInstance();\nc.set(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK,7);\nc.set(Calendar.WEEK_OF_MONTH,1);\nc.set(Calendar.MONTH,10);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>**\nwhen calling c.getTime();\ninstead of getting the first Saturday of November  i am getting the last Saturday of october?<\/p>\n",
